      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OCEAN'S PEARL (7) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only half a length (17.59) behind Fabio Zed at this track. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with four wins from six starts. Leading chance again. TRALEE AIMEE (2) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at this track over 300m behind Al Can Do (18.09) in a Grade 4. Has ability and can measure up. FUN EFFECTS (1) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 5 winner three back (17.72) at this track over 300m. Well placed here and should do much better. KARLI MULWEE (3) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
